    <entry>
      <title>Salamin-Brent算法</title>
      <link href="/2021/10/10/Salamin-Brent%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95/"/>
      <url>/2021/10/10/Salamin-Brent%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><strong>Salamin-Brent算法</strong>:$令a_0=1,b_0=s_0=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}},并用递推公式$<br>$$a_n=\frac{a_{n-1}+b_{n-1}}{2},$$<br>$$b_n=\sqrt{a_{n-1}b_{n-1}},$$<br>$$s_n=s_{n-1}-2^n(a_n^2-b_n^2),$$<br>$$p_n=\frac{2a_n^2}{s_n}$$<br>$作迭代，则{p_n}二阶收敛于\pi$</p>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> 算法 </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> $\pi$ </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
  
  
    
    
